#  Minor Project Ideas for AI/ML Students


---

## ðŸ“Š  Data Analysis & Visualization Projects  

### Beginner Level
1.  Personal Finance Tracker Dashboard 
   - Track expenses, visualize spending patterns, predict monthly savings
   - Tech: Python, Pandas, Matplotlib, Streamlit

2.  COVID-19 Data Analyzer 
   - Real-time analysis of vaccination rates, cases by region
   - Tech: Pandas, Plotly, APIs

3.  Weather Pattern Visualizer 
   - Historical weather data analysis and trend visualization
   - Tech: Pandas, Seaborn, OpenWeatherMap API

4.  Student Grade Predictor 
   - Predict final grades based on assignment scores and attendance
   - Tech: Pandas, NumPy, basic regression

5.  Social Media Engagement Analyzer 
   - Analyze post engagement patterns (likes, shares, best posting times)
   - Tech: Pandas, Matplotlib, Twitter/Instagram API

---

## ðŸ”®  Regression & Prediction Projects  

### Beginner-Intermediate Level
6.  Laptop Price Predictor 
   - Predict laptop prices based on specifications (RAM, processor, brand)
   - Tech: Linear Regression, Pandas, Flask for web app

7.  Electricity Bill Forecaster 
   - Predict monthly electricity consumption and cost
   - Tech: Multiple Linear Regression, historical usage data

8.  Uber/Ola Fare Estimator 
   - Predict ride fare based on distance, time, traffic
   - Tech: Linear Regression, Google Maps API

9.  Restaurant Revenue Predictor 
   - Predict daily/weekly revenue based on factors like weather, events
   - Tech: Regression, Feature Engineering

10.  Crop Yield Prediction System 
    - Predict agricultural yield based on soil, weather, fertilizer data
    - Tech: Regression, real agricultural datasets

11.  Real Estate Price Analyzer 
    - Predict house prices by location, size, amenities
    - Tech: Multiple Regression, web scraping for data

12.  Student Exam Score Predictor 
    - Predict exam scores based on study hours, past performance
    - Tech: Logistic Regression for pass/fail, Linear for scores

---

## ðŸŽ¯  Classification Projects  

### Intermediate Level
13.  Email Spam Classifier 
    - Classify emails as spam/not spam
    - Tech: Naive Bayes, TF-IDF, NLP basics

14.  Diabetes Risk Predictor 
    - Predict diabetes risk based on health parameters
    - Tech: Logistic Regression, SVM, Decision Tree

15.  Credit Card Fraud Detector 
    - Detect fraudulent transactions in real-time
    - Tech: Random Forest, imbalanced data handling

16.  Student Dropout Prediction 
    - Predict which students might dropout based on attendance, grades
    - Tech: Decision Tree, Random Forest

17.  Plant Disease Identifier 
    - Classify plant diseases from leaf images
    - Tech: KNN, image features, later upgrade to CNN

18.  Customer Segmentation Tool 
    - Segment customers by purchasing behavior
    - Tech: K-Means clustering, feature engineering

19.  Loan Approval Predictor 
    - Predict loan approval chances based on applicant data
    - Tech: Logistic Regression, Decision Tree

20.  Resume Screening System 
    - Classify resumes by job fit
    - Tech: NLP, Classification algorithms

21.  Fake News Detector (Text-based) 
    - Classify news articles as real or fake
    - Tech: NLP, Random Forest, TF-IDF

22.  Heart Disease Predictor 
    - Predict heart disease risk from medical parameters
    - Tech: SVM, Random Forest, medical datasets

---

## ðŸ›’  Recommender System Projects  

### Intermediate Level
23.  Movie Recommendation Engine 
    - Recommend movies based on user preferences
    - Tech: Collaborative filtering, content-based filtering

24.  Book Recommender System 
    - Suggest books based on reading history
    - Tech: Content-based filtering, Goodreads API

25.  Music Playlist Generator 
    - Create personalized playlists
    - Tech: Collaborative filtering, Spotify API

26.  E-commerce Product Recommender 
    - "Customers who bought this also bought..."
    - Tech: Association rules, collaborative filtering

27.  Job Recommender System 
    - Match job seekers with suitable positions
    - Tech: Content-based filtering, skills matching

28.  Restaurant Recommendation App 
    - Suggest restaurants based on cuisine, location, ratings
    - Tech: Hybrid recommendation, Zomato API

---

## ðŸ’¬  NLP & Sentiment Analysis Projects  

### Intermediate Level
29.  Product Review Sentiment Analyzer 
    - Analyze Amazon/Flipkart reviews (positive/negative/neutral)
    - Tech: NLP, VADER/TextBlob, visualization

30.  Social Media Sentiment Tracker 
    - Track brand sentiment on Twitter in real-time
    - Tech: Twitter API, NLP, sentiment analysis

31.  Customer Feedback Analyzer 
    - Analyze customer support tickets and categorize by sentiment
    - Tech: NLP, classification, topic modeling

32.  News Article Summarizer 
    - Automatically summarize long news articles
    - Tech: NLP, extractive summarization

33.  Hate Speech Detector 
    - Detect toxic/hate comments on social media
    - Tech: NLP, classification, BERT (advanced)

34.  Chatbot for FAQ (Rule-based) 
    - Answer common questions about a product/service
    - Tech: NLP, pattern matching, intent classification

35.  Voice of Customer Dashboard 
    - Aggregate and visualize customer feedback from multiple sources
    - Tech: NLP, sentiment analysis, dashboards

---

## ðŸ§   Deep Learning Projects  

### Intermediate-Advanced Level
36.  Handwritten Digit Recognizer 
    - Recognize handwritten digits (MNIST)
    - Tech: ANN, TensorFlow/Keras

37.  Face Mask Detection System 
    - Detect if a person is wearing a mask
    - Tech: CNN, image classification, OpenCV

38.  Traffic Sign Recognition 
    - Classify traffic signs for autonomous vehicles
    - Tech: CNN, German Traffic Sign dataset

39.  Dog vs Cat Classifier 
    - Classic image classification problem
    - Tech: CNN, transfer learning (VGG16, ResNet)

40.  Pneumonia Detection from X-Rays 
    - Detect pneumonia from chest X-ray images
    - Tech: CNN, medical imaging dataset

